Check out Meetups in Toronto that cover any of these topics:
Javascript
Python
Devops
Machine Learning 

you never know which are the good ones - most are just social events but they get your head into the developer mindset. You might also get to get acquaintances in the software space.

https://www.meetup.com/topics/softwaredev/ca/on/toronto/
- the google one
- https://www.meetup.com/DevOpsTO/
- https://www.meetup.com/toronto-node-js/  (yes make sure Node.js is part of your javascript development - you need this to write server code)
- https://www.meetup.com/Python-Toronto/
- https://www.meetup.com/torontojs/
